data.name: Goal Globe: European Football
data.description: Goal Globe is a European football live score website provides all the real-time updates on all the latest football matches and scores across the continent. You can also interact with people.

data.name: YASMP: Yet Another Social Media Platform
data.description: YASMP is React based Instagram clone that lets users establish their profile and publish their content in many genres, allowing them to share posts and interact with a group of like-minded individuals.

data.name: Efficient Search Engine
data.description: This project develops an efficient search engine designed to provide relevant search results. Leveraging advanced algorithms, it indexes web content meticulously, prioritizes high-quality information, and optimizes responses to user queries, offering an unparalleled browsing experience.

data.name: AURA: Australian Rainfall Prediction
data.description: The project enables us to predict whether or not a location in Australia will experience rain tomorrow using the weather observation data. Given a set of features, we want to predict the target variable RainTomorrow as, 1 which shows either it will rain the next day or 0 which shows it will not rain the next day.
